          { "feature": "splenomegaly", "weight": 3 },
          { "feature": "hepatomegaly", "weight": 2 }
        ],
        "management": "Supportive: rest, hydration, analgesia. Avoid amoxicillin (causes rash). Monitor for airway obstruction. Corticosteroids if severe edema. Avoid contact sports for 4-6 weeks."
